# Weekly Notes

## 2026-05-23

- Review local edits with `notion-md status packages/@overeng/notion-md/demo/workspace --recursive`.
- Sync the folder only after each page has a distinct Notion page id.
- Restart watch mode after adding new `.nmd` files because recursive watch resolves its file set at startup.
